channel.title: Free Core FTP
channel.description:
Hello girls (and guys), I want to share a program that i always use to upload/download files to/from the internet. The program is called Core FTP.
Core FTP is a professional FTP (File Transfer Protocol) program.
Now, i want you to share the experience with me. So i am giving away serials for free. I will pay for them myself. I am not using a Keymaker (Or whatever those program things are called) or anything like that. Just a pure pay.
In order for me to pay to get the serial for you. You'll need to download Core FTP Pro Trial version from the official website. I suggest to use [url=http://www.google.com.au/]Google[/url] to search for it.
Now, you'll need to fill out this form and post it in a reply:[code]First Name: Surname: Core FTP Version:[/code]
You do not have to use your real first name or real surname. It is just required in the payment.
When the payment process is complete, you will receive a PM from me. It has the serial and identification information. The steps to install the serial will be in the PM too.
[b]NOTE:[/b] You will not receive your serial straight away. The payment takes a while to be processed, when i get the e-mail with the serial, then you'll receive a PM.
This is not a lie. Enjoy :).
~Time2Script
